   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00096-B-000-00225"/>Herrn <hi rend="latintype">Gustav Schwarzkopf</hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb207296"><hi rend="latintype">I. Tiefer
                        Graben 23</hi></rs>.</addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><p><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-00096-B-000-00226"/><salute>Lieber Gu<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tav,</salute> we<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c> Sie <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L04124-1"/><date>morgen</date><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L04124-1">Das erlaubt die Datierung auf den Vortag des
                     Poststempels.</note> 1) in <rs type="place" ref="#pmb587">Wiener Neu<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tadt</rs> <c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chlafen
               2) die <rs type="event" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb143121"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb2252">Medelsky</rs> als <rs type="work" ref="#pmb29917" subtype="implied">Chri<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tine</rs> in d <rs type="work" ref="#pmb29917">Liebelei</rs></rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><add place="above"><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehn</add> 3.) mit
               mir, <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L04124-2"/><rs type="person" ref="#pmb11740">Hugo</rs> und vielleicht noch <rs type="person" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb10863">andern</rs><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L04124-2">Neben
                  <rs type="person" ref="#pmb11740">Hofmannsthal</rs> kam nur noch <rs type="person" ref="#pmb10863">Richard Beer-Hofmann</rs> mit, <rs type="person" ref="#pmb12740">Schwarzkopf</rs> nicht.</note> zu<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>a<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c>en <c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ein wollen,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>o versa<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c>eln Sie <c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ich um 4.30 (morgen <date>Din<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tag</date>) am <rs type="place" ref="#pmb132">Südbahnhof</rs>.</p><closer>Herzlichen Gru<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>s Ihr<lb/><signed>Arthur</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
